sentences: Rankin won The Music Producers Guild Award for Breakthrough Engineer of the Year in 2010.
In 2012, Rankin won two Grammy Awards: in the Album of the Year category with Adele's 21, and Record of the Year category with "Rolling in the Deep".
In 2014, he was nominated for The Music Producers Guild Award for Engineer of the Year.
Mark Rankin is a music producer and engineer currently working in Los Angeles.
Rankin was born in England, now resided with family and kids in Los Angeles.
